  "main": "<main id=\"main\">\n\n  <section id=\"top\" class=\"pec-svc-hero\">\n    <div class=\"pec-svc-hero__inner\">\n      <div class=\"pec-svc-hero__grid\">\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"pec-hero__eyebrow\"><span class=\"pec-dot\"></span> Email preferences</div>\n          <h1 class=\"pec-h1\">Manage Your <span class=\"pec-h1__accent\">Email Preferences</span>.</h1>\n          <p class=\"pec-svc-hero__sub\">You are in control of what you receive from us. Update your preferences below or unsubscribe from all emails. No questions asked.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pec-svc-hero__media\">\n          <div class=\"pec-svc-hero__art\"><span class=\"pec-svc-hero__chip\">No friction</span><img src=\"../img/home-empathy.jpg\" alt=\"Pet Emergency Center reception area\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"pec-narr pec-narr--tint\">\n    <div class=\"pec-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"pec-eyebrow\">Granular preferences</div>\n      <h2 class=\"pec-h2\">Choose What You Want to Receive.</h2>\n      <p>We send a few different types of emails. If you want to keep some and stop others, you can update your preferences here.</p>\n      <form class=\"pec-form\" method=\"POST\" action=\"#\" style=\"max-width:none\">\n        <div class=\"pec-form__row\" style=\"gap:16px\">\n          <label style=\"display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer\">\n            <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"seasonal_tips\" value=\"1\" style=\"margin-top:6px;width:20px;height:20px;flex:0 0 auto\">\n            <span><strong style=\"display:block;color:var(--pec-ink);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px\">Seasonal Health Tips</strong>Once a month, we share the seasonal pet health tip that matters most for South Florida pet owners right now. Heatstroke, hurricane prep, cane toads, holiday hazards. Useful, brief, no fluff.</span>\n          </label>\n          <label style=\"display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer\">\n            <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"recovery_stories\" value=\"1\" style=\"margin-top:6px;width:20px;height:20px;flex:0 0 auto\">\n            <span><strong style=\"display:block;color:var(--pec-ink);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px\">Pet Recovery Stories</strong>Occasional emails featuring real recovery stories from patients we have treated, shared with permission. Heartwarming, not promotional.</span>\n          </label>\n          <label style=\"display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer\">\n            <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"practice_updates\" value=\"1\" style=\"margin-top:6px;width:20px;height:20px;flex:0 0 auto\">\n            <span><strong style=\"display:block;color:var(--pec-ink);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px\">Practice Updates</strong>Occasional updates about hours, services, and changes that may affect how you reach us.</span>\n          </label>\n          <label style=\"display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer\">\n            <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"promotional\" value=\"1\" style=\"margin-top:6px;width:20px;height:20px;flex:0 0 auto\">\n            <span><strong style=\"display:block;color:var(--pec-ink);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px\">Promotional Emails</strong>Information about telehealth services, payment options, and similar offerings. Never sales-heavy, but if you would rather not receive these, you can opt out.</span>\n          </label>\n        </div>\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"pec-btn pec-btn--primary pec-btn--lg pec-form__submit\">Save My Preferences</button>\n      </form>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"pec-narr\">\n    <div class=\"pec-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"pec-eyebrow\">Or leave entirely</div>\n      <h2 class=\"pec-h2\">Or Unsubscribe From All.</h2>\n      <p>If you would prefer to stop receiving all emails from Pet Emergency Center, that is okay. Click the button below and we will remove you from every list immediately.</p>\n      <form method=\"POST\" action=\"#\">\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"pec-btn pec-btn--outline pec-btn--lg\">Unsubscribe From All Emails</button>\n      </form>\n      <p style=\"margin-top:12px;color:var(--pec-muted);font-size:14px\">One click. Removes you from all lists immediately.</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"pec-narr pec-narr--center\">\n    <div class=\"pec-wrap\">\n      <h2 class=\"pec-h2\">We Get It.</h2>\n      <p>Inboxes are crowded, and we appreciate every minute someone gives us. <strong>If you ever want to come back, you can resubscribe from any of our pages.</strong> Thank you for the time you have already given us.</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n</main>"
}
